title: Ep - 122 - JESSE MEESTER FROM 90 DAY FIANCÉ
description:
Jesse Meester from TLC’s “90 Day Fiancé” talks about his turbulent relationship with Darcey Silva, his life before the show, and what it is like to see your relationship play back on television. 


Podcast hosts Matt Marr and Jake Anthony review this week’s episode of Real Housewives of Dallas.
